{
  "stem": "11797.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't common for a Jewish person to walk around the streets like this, you know, because you probably would get beaten up by youngsters.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably '38.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was already 13 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My-- I had an uncle that lived probably about a couple of miles-- we lived, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I used to-- and I used to go up there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I used to look all over, look around if somebody's going to do something to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Very seldom-- there were also parks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We used to go to a park, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was afraid to go in the park because maybe I might get beaten up there, too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only, only with Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jewish people, we used to play soccer, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to play chess, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I used to love to make little small shows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was very nice to put on shows, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We used to invite-- but we used to charge $0.10 a ticket.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We used to come in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my brother used to-- used to put on some kind of funny thing, you know, and dressed up somebody, like a clown, be like a clown. you know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We used to sell lemonade on the street, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We used to sell bagels on the street, you know, to make-- just to make money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we, we, we were quite afraid when he heard that the Germans Jews are being thrown out from, from Germany and being chased into Poland, of course.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I saw something-- when I began to see new faces in my school, I noticed right away that something-- a change going on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they chased out the Jews from Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they came to Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they assigned them to my classes.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
